                        <p><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="3" color="black"><DIV>
                           <DIV><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif size=2>Burnside's North Carolina Expedition [February-June 1862]</FONT></DIV>
                           <DIV><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
                           <DIV><FONT size=2><SPAN class=quote_text><FONT size=2><I>"The enterprise of running the blockade and importing army supplies
                           from abroad has proven a complete success." </I></FONT><FONT size=2><a href="http://thomaslegion.net/zebulonbairdvance.html" target="tlx_new"><font  color="black"><FONT color=#0000ff>Governor Zebulon Baird Vance</FONT></font></a>, November 1863</FONT></SPAN></FONT>
                           <!--"''"--></DIV></DIV></font>
