                        <p><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="3" color="black"><DIV>
                           <P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=2>(February 8, 1862, map reflecting the forts and batteries located
                           on, and adjacent,&nbsp;the strategic Roanoke Island.)</FONT>
                           <!--"''"--></P></DIV></font>
